libparserutils (0.2.0) stable; urgency=medium

  - Fix memmove beyond buffer length in parserutlis_buffer_discard.  Thanks to Elie Roudninski.
  - Add test for memmove beyond buffer length, in parserutils_buffer_discard.
  - Replace use of abort() with assertions.
  - Fix non-iconv build.
  - add support for multilib
  - Fix bounds checking. Fixes CID 1152178, 1152179.
  - Fix leak.  Thanks to Ralf Junker.
  - Remove client allocation function.
  - Don't use the nonportable alloca() during tests.

